These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, december, september, april, may, october, june
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is the argentine##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Birthday           | may | april | december | september | march | october | june |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

