.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: lavender, white, blood-red, aquamarine, red, ivory, mauve
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes white is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Color          | lavender | white | red | aquamarine | ivory | mauve | blood-red |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

