.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, airplane, tram, roller, helicopter, snowmobile
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the bartender is the person driving the roller##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is the photographer##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Transport   | jet-ski | roller     | airplane  | helicopter       | train       | snowmobile  | tram   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

