.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, indie, jazz, metal, r&b, rock
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, photography, traveling, fishing, writing, filmmaking, reading
 1. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the fan of folk##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | rock     | jazz     | indie      | folk | metal      | disco     |
| Hobby   | fishing | traveling | filmmaking | writing | reading | photography | board-games |

