 3. the person traveling to hannover is in the middle##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| City     | nizza   | new-york    | marseilles | hannover     | prague         | liverpool     | edinburgh        |

