 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the nurse##1
 6. the designer is on the left of the nurse##1
 7. the coach is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 9. the designer is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the coach is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | time-travel | drama | martial-arts | satire     | animation | crime |
| Job     | architect | manager      | designer | nurse    | paramedic | firefighter   | coach  |

