.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
City: colone, san-francisco, edinburgh, miami, marseilles, liverpool, london
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | grapes | kiwi     | radish | watermelon | papaya |
| City   | liverpool | miami  | london    | colone | marseilles | san-francisco       | edinburgh   |

