 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
11. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Food          | raspberry | lime     | spinach | pepper | peas      | tomato  | potato |
| Color   | ivory   | ebony | blue  | amber | green | lavender | blood-red   |

